# 5. 编辑器/IDE 相关
# ==============================================
# VSCode
.vscode/
!.vscode/extensions.json  # 可选：如果想共享推荐插件，取消注释这行
*.code-workspace

# Visual Studio (VS)
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.vcxproj.user

# JetBrains 全家桶 (PyCharm/IDEA/CLion)
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
out/

# ==============================================
